content:
你最可爱的偶像小冷到台场来玩辣～
Your cutest idol Xiaoleng just came back from a travel to Odaiba~

Love Live联动的等身立牌超喜欢，小冷也会有像她们一样有名气的那一天吧？
I really liked the Love Live collaborated cardboard cutouts; there'll also be a day when I'll be famous just like them, right?

小冷有和你们一起实现的奇迹；2022年11月23日，我在日本东京Yoani Live Station的debut live上等你
By together our miracle comes true. November 23 2022, I'll be awaiting you at my debut concert at Yoani Live Station which located in Tokyo, Japan
